overview: Oyetayo Fred is the founder and CEO of Fresible Corporations, which he started in his high school in 2004. Oyetayo is responsible for setting the overall direction and product strategy for Fresible Corporations. He leads the Graphic design unit and Web Development section of Fresible Corporations and he is also for the service and development of its core technology and infrastructure. Earlier in life, Oyetayo developed a Picture recommendation system called FacAvhil. However, he abandoned it to pursue new projects. Oyetayo is currently in his Sophomore year as a law student at Afe Babalola University. While at Afe Babalola, Oyetayo created FacAvhil, a website that compared studentsâ€™ dorm photos side-by-side in a fashion similar to HOT or NOT. He also created a Technology Blog called Techie Magazine while he was in his third year.
